[DhtmlXQ_comment0]sg 20121025 1984 KunHua Cup GM Hu RongHua W GM Zhao GuoRong D40||||ECCO:D40 ??????????||ECCO: D40 Central Cannon vs Left 3 Step Tiger with Opposite Direction Cannons Variation ||Jim: This game was played way back in 1984. Two sure futrure Hall of Famers met at the KunHua Cup whereby only Masters and GMs were allowed to participate. This game was recently re-published in a recent edition of Xiangqi. And because of this game, there were great changes to black's opening.||Comments were from the magazine. Master Huang Shaolong had also commented on this game in one of this books. I have combined the comments for greater indepth study into this variation. Additional footnotes have been added to help beginners grasp the principles demonstrated.[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
